(9, 'com_content.article.5', '', '2024-12-20 15:19:03', 642, 11608, '96856b3477c8c338ca612b0fc25548278d3346a0', '{\"id\":5,\"asset_id\":122,\"title\":\"Th\\u1eddi trang Y3K b\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed5\",\"alias\":\"th-i-trang-y3k-bung-n\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Ca s\\u0129 Lisa v\\u00e0 gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb y\\u00eau th\\u1eddi trang l\\u0103ng x\\u00ea trang ph\\u1ee5c mang y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eefng n\\u0103m 3000.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Theo\\u00a0<em>Vogue<\\/em>, Y3K g\\u00e2y s\\u1ed1t tr\\u00ean\\u00a0<em>TikTok<\\/em>\\u00a0trong nh\\u1eefng th\\u00e1ng g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e2y. Xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c truy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00f4i sao c\\u00f3 t\\u1ea7m \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng l\\u1edbn nh\\u01b0\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/chu-de\\/lisa-3659\\\" rel=\\\"dofollow\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_LangMot-4807463&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-Lisa&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">Lisa<\\/a> c\\u1ee7a Blackpink, nh\\u00f3m nh\\u1ea1c H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c Aespa v\\u00e0 NewJeans, nh\\u00f3m nh\\u1ea1c Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n XG. Tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u ho\\u1eb7c trong c\\u00e1c MV, h\\u1ecd th\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ea1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c chi ti\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u1ea5y trong tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed v\\u00e0 phim khoa h\\u1ecdc vi\\u1ec5n t\\u01b0\\u1edfng theo ki\\u1ec3u cyberpunk.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2024\\/10\\/23\\/lisa-4799-1729662623.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Cex4cqC5nNiKn9a0_K8JLQ\\\" alt=\\\"Lisa di\\u1ec7n phong c\\u00e1ch Y3K v\\u1edbi thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 m\\u1ed1t Vi\\u1ec7t (tr\\u00e1i) khi bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n n\\u0103m 2023 v\\u00e0 trong b\\u1ed9 \\u1ea3nh qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 MV Rockstar. \\u1ea2nh: Instagram Lisa\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Y3K l\\u00e0 t\\u1eeb vi\\u1ebft t\\u1eaft cho \\\"Year 3000\\\", l\\u00e0 thu\\u1eadt ng\\u1eef m\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 phong c\\u00e1ch th\\u1eddi trang c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng n\\u0103m 3000. Trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u0111i theo m\\u1ed1t n\\u00e0y th\\u01b0\\u1eddng mang ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u kim lo\\u1ea1i ho\\u1eb7c gi\\u1ea3 kim, b\\u1ea3ng m\\u00e0u neon v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u00e1y \\u00e1o m\\u00e0i b\\u1ea1c, qu\\u1ea7n cargo nhi\\u1ec1u t\\u00fai v\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 kh\\u1ed5, \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c vinyl, v\\u00e1y \\u00e1o cao su t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p trang s\\u1ee9c 3D. \\u0110\\u1ec3 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf th\\u01b0\\u1eddng khai th\\u00e1c tri\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 AI trong s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Agus Panzoni, chuy\\u00ean gia nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u1ee7a Depop - c\\u00f4ng ty th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed M\\u1ef9 - n\\u00f3i v\\u1edbi\\u00a0<em>Refinery29<\\/em>: \\\"Ch\\u00fang ta \\u0111\\u00e3 ch\\u1ee9ng ki\\u1ebfn AI b\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed5 trong v\\u00e0i n\\u0103m qua v\\u00e0 khi th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ed1 h\\u00f3a, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 g\\u00ec ng\\u1ea1c nhi\\u00ean khi th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 Z - nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi nh\\u1ea1y b\\u00e9n v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 - l\\u1ea1i l\\u0103ng x\\u00ea nhi\\u1ec7t t\\u00ecnh cho th\\u1eddi trang l\\u1ea5y c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c n\\u00e0y\\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Theo Panzoni, c\\u00e1c t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm v\\u1ec1 \\\"Y3K\\\" tr\\u00ean Depop \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u0103ng 250% k\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1ea7u n\\u0103m. Tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng\\u00a0<em>Pinterest<\\/em>, thu\\u1eadt ng\\u1eef n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea1t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm t\\u0103ng g\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u00f4i t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 5, cho th\\u1ea5y nhu c\\u1ea7u cao c\\u1ee7a gen Z v\\u00e0 th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 Millennials (gen Y, sinh trong kho\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u th\\u1eadp ni\\u00ean 1980 gi\\u1eefa th\\u1eadp ni\\u00ean 1990).<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\\"sis_outstream__c\\\" data-set=\\\"dfp\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">D\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u v\\u00e0 kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a\\u00a0<em>Pinterest\\u00a0<\\/em>t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 9\\/2020 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 9\\/2022 c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0a ra nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ed1 li\\u1ec7u ch\\u1ee9ng minh cho s\\u1ef1 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i c\\u1ee7a s\\u1edf th\\u00edch th\\u1eddi trang: l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm trang ph\\u1ee5c avant-garde t\\u0103ng 225%, trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ph\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 k\\u00ednh v\\u1ecb lai t\\u0103ng 70%, phong c\\u00e1ch game th\\u1ee7 (h\\u01a1i h\\u01b0\\u1edbng vi\\u1ec5n t\\u01b0\\u1edfng) t\\u0103ng t\\u1edbi 3.370%.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">S\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi trong hai n\\u0103m qua \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u1eafp v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng m\\u1eabu thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf si\\u00eau th\\u1ef1c, vi\\u1ec5n t\\u01b0\\u1edfng qua s\\u1ef1 l\\u0103ng x\\u00ea c\\u1ee7a Dior, Prada, Schiaparelli. Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00f3, nhi\\u1ec1u nh\\u00e0 m\\u1ed1t t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u01b0a y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp nh\\u01b0 Pierre Cardin, Andr\\u00e9 Courr\\u00e8ges, Paco Rabanne, Thierry Mugler, Issey Miyake, Alexander McQueen, Nicolas Ghesqui\\u00e8re.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">Y3K kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 t\\u1ea1o ra t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng trong th\\u1eddi trang m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n \\u1edf l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1eb9p, tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng hot c\\u1ee7a m\\u00f9a l\\u1ea1nh n\\u0103m nay. Th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng hai n\\u0103m qua gia t\\u0103ng nhu c\\u1ea7u ph\\u1ea5n m\\u1eaft \\u00e1nh kim lo\\u1ea1i, nh\\u0169 m\\u00e0u b\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 thoa l\\u00ean tr\\u00e1n v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u00e3ng c\\u00f2n tung ra c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u00ednh l\\u00ean m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 th\\u00e1i d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u00ecnh tinh th\\u1ec3, v\\u1ea3y, m\\u00f3ng vu\\u1ed1t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u1ea5y trong th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi si\\u00eau th\\u1ef1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2024\\/10\\/23\\/lam-dep-y3k-1526-1729662624.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=8jFcI_bofz8mtIQDk6E44w\\\" alt=\\\"Di\\u1ec5n vi\\u00ean Florence Pugh (tr\\u00e1i) t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i ra m\\u1eaft Dune 2 \\u1edf London v\\u1edbi eyeliner kim lo\\u1ea1i.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1ea7u n\\u0103m t\\u1edbi nay, c\\u00e1c s\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e0ng gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed, ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt ch\\u1ee9ng ki\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a phong c\\u00e1ch n\\u00e0y. Th\\u00e1ng 2, Zendaya m\\u1eb7c b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ed3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u00e1y bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ee7a Mugler \\u0111\\u1ebfn bu\\u1ed5i\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/thoi-trang-pha-cach-cua-sao-dune-zendaya-4712045.html\\\" rel=\\\"dofollow\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_LangMot-4807463&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-RaMatDune2&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">ra m\\u1eaft\\u00a0<em>Dune\\u00a0<\\/em>2<\\/a>, cho th\\u1ea5y qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o c\\u1ed5 \\u0111i\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111i tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea1i. T\\u1ea1i\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/tag\\/met-gala-2024-1643411\\\" rel=\\\"dofollow\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_LangMot-4807463&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-MetGala&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">Met Gala<\\/a>, v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 Khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn th\\u1eddi gian, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu Paloma Elsesser di\\u1ec7n corset kim lo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00ednh hoa l\\u00e0m b\\u1eb1ng k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt in 3D c\\u1ee7a H&amp;M. Nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u1ed9 trang ph\\u1ee5c kh\\u00e1c c\\u0169ng l\\u1ea5y c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb khoa h\\u1ecdc vi\\u1ec5n t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ea7m Balenciaga m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a Serena Williams g\\u1ee3i nh\\u1edb \\u0111\\u1ebfn robot, v\\u00e1y Marc Jacobs ph\\u1ea3n chi\\u1ebfu kim lo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a Venus Williams t\\u1ef1a b\\u1ee9c tranh mang nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u1ea3nh gh\\u00e9p v\\u1ec1 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Tr\\u00ean\\u00a0<em>Metro<\\/em>, stylist Anh Susie Hasler l\\u00fd gi\\u1ea3i v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ef1 b\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed5 c\\u1ee7a Y3K: \\\"Th\\u1eddi trang 2023 v\\u00e0 2024 mang t\\u00ednh b\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u1eb7t, ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n kh\\u00e1c nh\\u1eefng n\\u0103m \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ecbch. B\\u1ed1i c\\u1ea3nh kinh t\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi suy tho\\u00e1i, h\\u1ed7n lo\\u1ea1n d\\u1eabn t\\u1edbi t\\u00e2m l\\u00fd ti\\u00eau c\\u1ef1c c\\u1ee7a con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ebb. T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3, h\\u1ecd s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eefng trang ph\\u1ee5c c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea7n n\\u1ed5i lo\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1eadm ch\\u1ea5t punk v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf ph\\u1ea3n \\u00e1nh cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai d\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1eb7c chi ti\\u1ebft li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7, nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 an to\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n d\\u1ee5ng\\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Theo\\u00a0<em>Elle<\\/em>, xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng n\\u00e0y cho ph\\u00e9p m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ef1 do k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p trang ph\\u1ee5c theo \\u00fd th\\u00edch v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u1eafp tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 nh\\u00e2n t\\u1ea1o. Gi\\u1edbi y\\u00eau th\\u1eddi trang c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng nh\\u1eefng m\\u00f3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1eadm ch\\u1ea5t Y2K, ph\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng nh\\u1eefng ph\\u1ee5 ki\\u1ec7n v\\u1ecb lai nh\\u01b0 k\\u00ednh Matrix, sneakers chunky m\\u00e0u b\\u1ea1c, trang s\\u1ee9c l\\u1ea5y c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb linh ki\\u1ec7n \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed, m\\u00e1y m\\u00f3c.<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:19:03\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:19:03\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:19:03\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(10, 'com_content.article.6', '', '2024-12-20 15:24:06', 642, 7274, '8739e2bb4140591ac244794385b8d6bf82c75af1', '{\"id\":6,\"asset_id\":123,\"title\":\"B\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp v\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi c\\u1ee7a NTK Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh t\\u1ea1i Fashion Voyage No.5\",\"alias\":\"b-suu-t-p-vay-cu-i-c-a-ntk-phuong-linh-t-i-fashion-voyage-no-5\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh ra m\\u1eaft b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp \\\"La Rosa\\\" t\\u1ea1i Fashion Voyage No.5, g\\u1eedi g\\u1eafm d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c m\\u1eabu v\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi theo phong c\\u00e1ch n\\u1eef t\\u00ednh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image001-7805-1682050558.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=OPrLk0Zhy4T5gA9TSC7pmA\\\" alt=\\\"Bu\\u1ed5i tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n di\\u1ec5n ra trong khu\\u00f4n kh\\u1ed5 show di\\u1ec5n Fashion Voyage No.5. D\\u00e0n m\\u1eabu s\\u1ea3i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc tr\\u00ean c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n (Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c), g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n tinh th\\u1ea7n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image002-4539-1682050558.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=I_jkbJ39jIxJYXzWK7Vvtw\\\" alt=\\\"V\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00f2i h\\u1ecfi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n k\\u1ef9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v\\u00e0 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c kh\\u1eaft khe. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, show di\\u1ec5n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb k\\u1ef9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng trong nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image003-9045-1682050558.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=yjELwu4j6ye_lyP_C3g9Fw\\\" alt=\\\"Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp La Rosa v\\u1edbi ngu\\u1ed3n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n v\\u00e0 v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image004-6402-1682050558.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=98E1j56sIbhbjjwbCvGo1Q\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u00e1c m\\u1eabu thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf trong b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp La Rosa c\\u00f3 bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng xuy\\u00ean su\\u1ed1t l\\u00e0 hoa h\\u1ed3ng, \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n cho t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau, s\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 v\\u0129nh c\\u1eedu c\\u1ee7a t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau. Kh\\u00e1nh Linh cho bi\\u1ebft, b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp n\\u00e0y mang \\u0111\\u1eadm d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image005-7442-1682050558.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=LNiN0c__PXxhZ5B021bNSA\\\" alt=\\\"\\u0110i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng trong thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a NTK Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh l\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 l\\u00e3ng m\\u1ea1n, t\\u1ef1 do nh\\u01b0ng kh\\u00f4ng g\\u00f2 b\\u00f3 theo b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 quy chu\\u1ea9n th\\u1eddi trang n\\u00e0o. C\\u00f4 coi tr\\u1ecdng s\\u1ef1 tinh t\\u1ebf trong t\\u1eebng thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image006-3135-1682050559.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=xk-UKgvpU30YNJMlt6NQTQ\\\" alt=\\\"To\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp La Rosa l\\u00e0 v\\u1ea3i chiffon, organza, tulle, ren v\\u00e0 hoa ren 3D cao c\\u1ea5p do nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft l\\u1ebf Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1eeb Italy, Ph\\u00e1p.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image007-1499-1682050559.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=6Z-8NurtsG5nuYW1ZViK5g\\\" alt=\\\"\\u0110\\u1ec3 th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n tinh th\\u1ea7n c\\u1ee7a La Rosa, nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ba si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu Thanh H\\u1eb1ng, hoa h\\u1eadu HHen ni\\u00ea, hoa h\\u1eadu Ng\\u1ecdc Ch\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u1ea3m nhi\\u1ec7m vai tr\\u00f2 vedette. Nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 m\\u1edf m\\u00e0n cho show di\\u1ec5n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c giao cho V\\u0169 Ng\\u1ecdc Anh, \\u00c1 H\\u1eadu Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Anh.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image008-7543-1682050559.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=VMZVkVjdmgG-vDzc81y3Tw\\\" alt=\\\"Ch\\u1ee7 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u Calla Bridal l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn d\\u00e0n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1eb9p theo ti\\u00eau ch\\u00ed ngo\\u1ea1i h\\u00ecnh ng\\u1ecdt ng\\u00e0o, r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 nh\\u1eb1m th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng c\\u00f4 d\\u00e2u th\\u1ef1c th\\u1ee5 trong ng\\u00e0y tr\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/21\\/image009-6394-1682050559.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=ulQt-A1hzJRp5aJJmxoQGQ\\\" alt=\\\"La Rosa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1eb7t trong b\\u1ed1i c\\u1ea3nh m\\u00eanh m\\u00f4ng bi\\u1ec3n tr\\u1eddi, khung c\\u1ea3nh ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n - n\\u00e9t \\u0111\\u1eb9p \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng c\\u1ee7a Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c.\\\"><\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:24:06\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:24:06\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:24:06\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(11, 'com_content.article.7', '', '2024-12-20 15:26:01', 642, 11531, '43e6f9f48e45c2864f311aed97af26255b2b2fe9', '{\"id\":7,\"asset_id\":124,\"title\":\"VieON ph\\u00e1t l\\u1ea1i Fashion Voyage\",\"alias\":\"vieon-phat-l-i-fashion-voyage\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh Fashion Voyage 5 ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\\"Dating with a Kiss\\\" \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ed9c quy\\u1ec1n tr\\u00ean VieON v\\u00e0o 20h ng\\u00e0y 20\\/4 v\\u00e0 27\\/4.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\"><em>Fashion Voyage<\\/em>\\u00a0do Long Kan \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n, di\\u1ec5n ra t\\u1ea1i th\\u1ecb tr\\u1ea5n Ho\\u00e0ng H\\u00f4n, Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c, h\\u00f4m 8-9\\/4. S\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec7n c\\u00f3 g\\u00f3p m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf t\\u00ean tu\\u1ed5i c\\u00f9ng 400 kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n VieON nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh c\\u00f3 s\\u1ee9c h\\u00fat l\\u1edbn, kh\\u00f4ng gian ch\\u00ednh \\u1edf c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n (Kiss Bridge, d\\u00e0i 810 m) h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng r\\u00e1ng chi\\u1ec1u, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00e9t l\\u00e3ng m\\u1ea1n, thi v\\u1ecb. \\\"V\\u1edbi mong mu\\u1ed1n gi\\u00fap m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi theo d\\u00f5i l\\u1ea1i, tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m phong c\\u00e1ch th\\u01b0\\u1edfng l\\u00e3m th\\u1eddi trang m\\u1edbi, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ph\\u00e1t s\\u00f3ng Fashion Voyage\\\", ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb n\\u00f3i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/19\\/image001-2141-1681869613.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=f8VulmoUhfHEm6vbYoCS5Q\\\" alt=\\\"Thanh H\\u1eb1ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt \\u1edf showCTPNo2 c\\u1ee7a Chung Thanh Phong. Si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu ki\\u00eam Hoa h\\u1eadu ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef qua \\u1ea3nh 2001 gi\\u1eef v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed vedette, th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n trang ph\\u1ee5c tr\\u00e1ng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u00ecnh c\\u00e1nh b\\u01b0\\u1edbm.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Gi\\u1eefa khung c\\u1ea3nh n\\u00ean th\\u01a1 v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1t tr\\u1eafng, n\\u1eafng v\\u00e0ng \\u1edf bi\\u1ec3n xanh nam \\u0111\\u1ea3o Ng\\u1ecdc, show \\\"CTPNo2\\\" c\\u1ee7a\\u00a0<strong>Chung Thanh Phong<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u0111\\u01b0a kh\\u00e1n gi\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh tinh t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u1edbi trang ph\\u1ee5c phong c\\u00e1ch futuristic (v\\u1ecb lai). Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u 85 trang ph\\u1ee5c ph\\u00e1 c\\u00e1ch, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u1eabu s\\u1edf tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u00e1, mica tr\\u00e1ng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ean v\\u00e1y ng\\u1eafn, \\u0111\\u1ea7m qu\\u00e2y ng\\u1ef1c d\\u1ef1 ti\\u1ec7c, v\\u00e1y cut-out.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Lo\\u1ea1t hoa v\\u0103n ch\\u1eef l\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean t\\u1eeb h\\u1ea1t c\\u01b0\\u1eddm ho\\u1eb7c in, th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea7m su\\u00f4ng. Nhi\\u1ec1u phom d\\u00e1ng g\\u1ed3m \\u00e1o corset, ch\\u00e2n v\\u00e1y mini, \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c, \\u00e1o hoodie... s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt ch\\u1ea7n b\\u00f4ng v\\u1ea3i nh\\u0169 v\\u00e0 cotton pha.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Metallic - ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng c\\u1ee7a v\\u1ecb lai, \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0ng m\\u1ed1t qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf \\u01b0a chu\\u1ed9ng - \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Chung Thanh Phong l\\u0103ng x\\u00ea tr\\u00ean \\u00e1o cho\\u00e0ng, qu\\u1ea7n cargo, v\\u00e1y cut-out. H\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn gen Z, b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp c\\u00f2n mang t\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf denim \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd m\\u00e0i, t\\u1ea9y, nhu\\u1ed9m, x\\u00e9 c\\u00f4ng phu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Chung Thanh Phong ch\\u1ecdn Minh T\\u00fa m\\u1edf m\\u00e0n, si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu Thanh H\\u1eb1ng k\\u1ebft show. Nhi\\u1ec1u g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt kh\\u00e1c tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n c\\u00e1c v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed quan tr\\u1ecdng trong show nh\\u01b0 Ti\\u1ec3u Vy, Hoa h\\u1eadu chuy\\u1ec3n gi\\u1edbi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam 2020 Tr\\u00e2n \\u0110\\u00e0i, B\\u1ea3o Ng\\u1ecdc... D\\u00e0n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1eb9p s\\u1ea3i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u1edf s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n tr\\u00ean n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, mang d\\u00e1ng d\\u1ea5p d\\u1ea3i g\\u1ea5m v\\u1eaft ngang qua \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/19\\/image002-5100-1681869613.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=l8xRUAD13V-qrbtaYPHNFQ\\\" alt=\\\"- 1\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf\\u00a0<strong>Th\\u1ee7y Nguy\\u1ec5n\\u00a0<\\/strong>mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp\\u00a0<em>\\u1edai a \\u01a1i \\u00e0<\\/em>\\u00a0- truy\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3i c\\u00e2u chuy\\u1ec7n v\\u1ec1 v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a, truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng \\u00c1 \\u0110\\u00f4ng. \\u0110i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n show l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3nh hoa h\\u1eadu Ng\\u1ecdc Ch\\u00e2u n\\u1eafm tay m\\u1eb9 - b\\u00e0 \\u0110\\u1eb7ng Th\\u1ecb G\\u00e1i - \\u0111\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed vedette, s\\u1ea3i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc tr\\u00ean s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n d\\u00e0i 810 m.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\"><strong>Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh\\u00a0<\\/strong>th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n show v\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi\\u00a0<em>La Rosa\\u00a0<\\/em>\\u1edf n\\u01a1i ng\\u1eafm ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb9p nh\\u1ea5t - c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n, bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng t\\u1ea1i Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c. M\\u1ed7i trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u1ea9n \\u00fd s\\u1eafc th\\u00e1i t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau - t\\u1eeb ng\\u1ea1i ng\\u00f9ng, h\\u1eddn ghen \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u1ee5 h\\u00f4n n\\u1ed3ng ch\\u00e1y.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\\"sis_outstream__c\\\" data-set=\\\"dfp\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">B\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp m\\u1edbi ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c khai th\\u00e1c chiffon, organza, tulle, v\\u1ea3i ren v\\u00e0 hoa ren 3D t\\u1eebng - ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u quen thu\\u1ed9c g\\u1eafn v\\u1edbi nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m qua. Lo\\u1ea1t ph\\u1ee5 ki\\u1ec7n, ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1eeb Italy v\\u00e0 Ph\\u00e1p, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng, gi\\u00fap trang ph\\u1ee5c th\\u00eam s\\u1eafc n\\u00e9t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu, di\\u1ec5n vi\\u00ean V\\u0169 Ng\\u1ecdc Anh \\u0111\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed m\\u1edf m\\u00e0n, trong khi vedette l\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 ba H\\u2019Hen Ni\\u00ea, Thanh H\\u1eb1ng, Ng\\u1ecdc Ch\\u00e2u. T\\u1ea1i show n\\u00e0y, \\u00e1 h\\u1eadu Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Anh nh\\u1eadn l\\u1eddi c\\u1ea7u h\\u00f4n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n trai h\\u01a1n 4 tu\\u1ed5i - doanh nh\\u00e2n \\u0110\\u1ee9c H\\u1ed3. C\\u1ea3 hai l\\u00ean k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u00e1m c\\u01b0\\u1edbi trong n\\u0103m nay nh\\u01b0ng ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 th\\u1eddi gian.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9c gi\\u1ea3 nh\\u1eadp m\\u00e3 \\\"VieONVNP\\\" \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i, th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c show\\u00a0<em>Fashion Voyage<\\/em>\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/click.vieon.vn\\/k9pz\\/FashionVoyage\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/19\\/image003-8671-1681869614.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=b6yNQwqK4wJo_wjyY0FvHQ\\\" alt=\\\"ff\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">H\\u01a1n hai n\\u0103m ra m\\u1eaft, VieON - th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a DatVietVAC Group Holdings - \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 m\\u1ea1nh c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 l\\u1eabn n\\u1ed9i dung ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p m\\u1ecdi \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kh\\u00e1n gi\\u1ea3, gi\\u00fap ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u1ecdn ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p. \\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng cam k\\u1ebft x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng, ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kho gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed d\\u00e0nh cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t, kh\\u00f4ng ng\\u1eebng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00e1c phim g\\u1ed1c nh\\u01b0:\\u00a0<em>C\\u00e2y t\\u00e1o n\\u1edf hoa, Gi\\u1ea5c m\\u01a1 c\\u1ee7a m\\u1eb9, N\\u1eef ch\\u1ee7<\\/em>\\u00a0hay g\\u1ea7n nh\\u1ea5t\\u00a0<em>M\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi m\\u00f9a \\u0111\\u00f4ng<\\/em>\\u00a0v\\u00e0\\u00a0<em>Hoa v\\u01b0\\u01a1ng<\\/em>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">VieON c\\u00f2n khai th\\u00e1c, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t n\\u1ed9i dung trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p h\\u01a1i th\\u1edf th\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea1i, ph\\u1ea3n \\u00e1nh ch\\u00e2n th\\u1eadt, \\u0111a chi\\u1ec1u x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. \\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u0169ng mua b\\u1ea3n quy\\u1ec1n ph\\u00e1t s\\u00f3ng lo\\u1ea1t phim \\u0103n kh\\u00e1ch H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c, Th\\u00e1i Lan v\\u00e0 Hoa ng\\u1eef nh\\u01b0:\\u00a0<em>\\u1ed0c \\u0111\\u1ea3o tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb, Y\\u00eau l\\u00e0 \\u0111au, T\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau m\\u00e0 th\\u00f4i, L\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng b\\u1ea5t nghi, K\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u00e1nh c\\u1eafp b\\u00e1u v\\u1eadt, Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng nguy\\u1ec7t t\\u1eabn min<\\/em>h...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Nh\\u1eb1m mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ec9nh cao, VieON k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p SPT cung c\\u1ea5p c\\u00e1c g\\u00f3i c\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p hai d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 \\\"Internet v\\u00e0 truy\\u1ec1n h\\u00ecnh VieON\\\". Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, thu\\u00ea bao Internet SPT hi\\u1ec7n h\\u1eefu c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd th\\u00eam g\\u00f3i Basic \\u0111\\u1ebfn All Access v\\u1edbi gi\\u00e1 t\\u1eeb 20.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn 250.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng m\\u1ed9t th\\u00e1ng. Kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd ngay g\\u00f3i combo \\u0111\\u1ec3 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi gi\\u00e1 t\\u1eeb 165.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng m\\u1ed9t th\\u00e1ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng c\\u0169ng gi\\u1ea3m 25.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng cho kh\\u00e1ch mua g\\u00f3i d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 v\\u00e0 thanh to\\u00e1n b\\u1eb1ng VNPAY QR, \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1eeb nay \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u1ebft 20\\/5.<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:26:01\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:26:01\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:26:01\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);
