(12, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2024-12-20 15:28:19', 642, 11510, '490935bdb31b6efe163ab88bbcc12515a4f97a25', '{\"id\":8,\"asset_id\":125,\"title\":\"Sun Group t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111\\u1ed9c quy\\u1ec1n show th\\u1eddi trang Fashion Voyage No.5\",\"alias\":\"sun-group-tai-tr-d-c-quy-n-show-th-i-trang-fashion-voyage-no-5\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Fashion Voyage No.5 \\u0111\\u01b0a gi\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9 \\u0111i\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u1edbi do Sun Group ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1o t\\u1ea1i Sunset Town, Nam Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c trong kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n hai ng\\u00e0y 8 v\\u00e0 9\\/4.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<div class=\\\"header-content width_common\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Fashion Voyage No.5 \\u0111\\u01b0a gi\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9 \\u0111i\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u1edbi do Sun Group ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1o t\\u1ea1i Sunset Town, Nam Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c trong kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n hai ng\\u00e0y 8 v\\u00e0 9\\/4.<\\/p>\\r\\n<article class=\\\"fck_detail \\\">\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 show di\\u1ec5n th\\u1ee9 5 trong chu\\u1ed7i Fashion Voyage c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan. T\\u1eadp \\u0111o\\u00e0n Sun Group \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111\\u1ed9c quy\\u1ec1n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng anh t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a chuy\\u1ebfn vi\\u1ec5n du th\\u1eddi trang n\\u00e0y, ti\\u00ean phong \\u0111\\u01b0a tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt v\\u00e0 th\\u1eddi trang v\\u00e0o ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 du l\\u1ecbch.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Fashion Voyage No.5 \\u0111\\u00e3 thu h\\u00fat c\\u00f4ng ch\\u00fang quan t\\u00e2m theo d\\u00f5i tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng, m\\u1ea1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. \\u0110\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n 2 s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n truy\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3i th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau t\\u1ea1i hai c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u1edbi t\\u1ea1i Nam Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u00e0 s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u nh\\u1ea1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc Kiss The Stars v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n (Kiss Bridge).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">Ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a Voyage No.5 di\\u1ec5n ra tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u Kiss The Stars. M\\u1edf m\\u00e0n l\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp CTP No.2 c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Chung Thanh Phong, gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u nh\\u1eefng trang ph\\u1ee5c phong c\\u00e1ch Futuristic (ch\\u1ee7 ngh\\u0129a v\\u1ecb lai), t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng th\\u1eddi trang t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai. H\\u1ed9i t\\u1ee5 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p gi\\u1eefa \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u00e2m nh\\u1ea1c, Fashion Voyage No.5 ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean chuy\\u1ebfn du h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt, th\\u1eddi trang giao h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng kh\\u00f4ng gian tr\\u00e1ng l\\u1ec7 c\\u1ee7a ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac v\\u00e0 thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/14\\/0072fv5-foto-kiengcan-jpeg-168-3978-3680-1681464951.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=v_swZaNBb_FgngfM4FdsLQ\\\" alt=\\\"B\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp CTP No.2 c\\u1ee7a NTK Chung Thanh Phong t\\u1ea1i s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u Kiss The Stars. \\u1ea2nh: Fashion Voyage\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Chung Thanh Phong chia s\\u1ebb anh c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y \\\"r\\u1ea5t may m\\u1eafn khi c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n t\\u1ea1i m\\u1ed9t s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u l\\u1edbn v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0 Kiss The Stars. C\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh n\\u00e0y v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp c\\u1ee7a Chung Thanh Phong gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 sinh ra \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u00e0nh cho nhau. V\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi khi c\\u00f9ng Sun Group v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n t\\u1ea1i Fashion Voyage No.5\\\". \\u0110\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh tr\\u00ean s\\u00e0n catwalk l\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 g\\u00f3p m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng t\\u00ean tu\\u1ed5i \\u0111\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u00e1m c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e0ng m\\u1eabu Vi\\u1ec7t nh\\u01b0: hoa h\\u1eadu - si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu Thanh H\\u1eb1ng, hoa h\\u1eadu Ti\\u1ec3u Vy, hoa h\\u1eadu B\\u1ea3o Ng\\u1ecdc, si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu Minh T\\u00fa...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Trong ng\\u00e0y tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n th\\u1ee9 hai, \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n n\\u1eefa khi\\u1ebfn gi\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9 \\u0111i\\u1ec7u th\\u00e1n ph\\u1ee5c b\\u1edfi t\\u00e0i n\\u0103ng trong ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt s\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t khi t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean \\\"s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n th\\u1ebf k\\u1ef7\\\" ngay t\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n d\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang cho hai nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Th\\u1ee7y Nguy\\u1ec5n v\\u00e0 Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">C\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac s\\u01b0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Italy Marco Casamonti t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean nh\\u1eb1m t\\u00f4n vinh v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 giao h\\u00f2a gi\\u1eefa hai n\\u1ec1n v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a Vi\\u1ec7t - Italy. V\\u1edbi chi\\u1ec1u d\\u00e0i 810 m\\u00e9t c\\u00f9ng hai nh\\u00e1nh t\\u00e1ch bi\\u1ec7t v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n \\\"ch\\u1ea1m\\\" v\\u00e0o nhau \\u1edf ch\\u00ednh gi\\u1eefa, c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n \\u00f4m tr\\u1ecdn l\\u1ea5y to\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 v\\u00f9ng bi\\u1ec3n lam ng\\u1ecdc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/14\\/2674fv5-foto-kiengcan-jpeg-168-3891-4802-1681464951.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=uIFLQa9JfOtaTfzf8tx9bQ\\\" alt=\\\"Nh\\u1eefng thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf trong b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp \\u1edai a \\u01a1i \\u00e0 c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Th\\u1ee7y Nguy\\u1ec5n tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n. \\u1ea2nh: Fashion Voyage\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 trang ph\\u1ee5c c\\u1ee7a Th\\u1ee7y Nguy\\u1ec5n t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc ri\\u00eang b\\u1eb1ng hoa v\\u0103n, ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ee5a l\\u00e0, g\\u1ea5m v\\u00f3c mang \\u0111\\u1eadm d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a Vi\\u1ec7t v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng n\\u00e9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u00e2n hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, l\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p gi\\u1eefa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 h\\u01a1i th\\u1edf c\\u1ee7a th\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Trong khi \\u0111\\u00f3, nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Linh l\\u1ea1i \\u0111em \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc v\\u00e1y c\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\\"La Rosa\\\" \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c may t\\u1eeb v\\u1ea3i chiffon, organza, tulle, ren v\\u00e0 hoa ren 3D, v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u chi ti\\u1ebft th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng mang d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n, t\\u00f4n vinh n\\u00e9t \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c n\\u00e0ng d\\u00e2u.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/14\\/2525fv5-foto-kiengcan-jpeg-168-1502-5337-1681464951.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=kaAc7Y_UuRVFkDeBg8X1vA\\\" alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7u h\\u00f4n b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd c\\u1ee7a doanh nh\\u00e2n \\u0110\\u1ee9c H\\u1ed3 v\\u00e0 \\u00c1 h\\u1eadu Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Anh ngay tr\\u00ean c\\u1ea7u H\\u00f4n, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau t\\u1ea1i Nam Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c. \\u1ea2nh: Fashion Voyage\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Sau 5 n\\u0103m kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ecb th\\u1ebf, Fashion Voyage kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01a1n thu\\u1ea7n l\\u00e0 cu\\u1ed9c d\\u1ea1o ch\\u01a1i c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan qua c\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ee9c h\\u00fat v\\u00e0 t\\u1ea7m \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh trong gi\\u1edbi th\\u1eddi trang v\\u00e0 du l\\u1ecbch. \\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng chung c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u th\\u1eddi trang \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7u khi \\u0111\\u01b0a nh\\u1eefng s\\u00e0n runway g\\u1ea7n v\\u1edbi thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c kh\\u00f4ng gian ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt, ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">T\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng c\\u00e1c s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n thu h\\u00fat h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tham d\\u1ef1 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ecba h\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 \\\"\\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n\\\" c\\u1ee7a Fashion Voyage m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1edbi. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u0169ng gi\\u00fap Fashion Voyage v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t kh\\u1ecfi nh\\u1eefng s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean c\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u th\\u1eddi trang, qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 du l\\u1ecbch m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\\"sis_outstream__c\\\" data-set=\\\"dfp\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">C\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111\\u1ed9c quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a Sun Group v\\u00e0 Sun Property (Th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean t\\u1eadp \\u0111o\\u00e0n Sun Group), Fashion Voyage c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u m\\u1ef9 ph\\u1ea9m Menard, TST tourist, du thuy\\u1ec1n Ambassador, Long Beach Pearl, Jet Dentist, Vascara, Liti Florist, nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng: VieON, TikTok, ProwTech, Luxuo Group, L\\u2019Officiel Vi\\u1ec7t Nam... v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u00e1c N\\u00e0ng Th\\u01a1m Communication, Tr\\u1ea7n Film, Ki\\u1ebfng C\\u1eadn...<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:28:19\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:28:19\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:28:19\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"