(13, 'com_content.article.9', '', '2024-12-20 15:30:33', 642, 11420, 'df2b7e62c54ea3e9cf89a45f88b6f67c464cc6c2', '{\"id\":9,\"asset_id\":126,\"title\":\"Show th\\u1eddi trang v\\u1ecb lai c\\u1ee7a Chung Thanh Phong\",\"alias\":\"show-th-i-trang-v-lai-c-a-chung-thanh-phong\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Show \\\"CTPNo2\\\" c\\u1ee7a Chung Thanh Phong \\u0111\\u01b0a kh\\u00e1n gi\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh tinh t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u1edbi trang ph\\u1ee5c phong c\\u00e1ch futuristic (v\\u1ecb lai).<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n ra ng\\u00e0y 7\\/4 t\\u1ea1i Ph\\u00fa Qu\\u1ed1c, l\\u1ea5y c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ngo\\u00e0i h\\u00e0nh tinh. 17h45, khi m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi ch\\u1ea1m \\u0111\\u1ec9nh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t trong ba c\\u00e1nh c\\u1ed5ng v\\u00f2m tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u, m\\u1ed9t gi\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u1ecdc vang l\\u00ean trong l\\u00e0n kh\\u00f3i tr\\u1eafng: \\\"Ch\\u00e0o m\\u1eebng l\\u00ean chuy\\u1ebfn t\\u00e0u mang s\\u1ed1 hi\\u1ec7u CTPNo2 \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 h\\u00e0nh tinh CTP, n\\u01a1i c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p th\\u1eddi trang kh\\u00f4ng khu\\u00f4n m\\u1eabu\\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/08\\/batch-938A0256-2649-1680935380.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=yb7lcccDnZlk6soeiDBocQ\\\" alt=\\\"\\u00c1o qu\\u00e1 kh\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 corset \\u0111\\u1eadm ch\\u1ea5t Futuristic. \\u1ea2nh: Ho\\u00e0ng Ph\\u00fac\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">S\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u h\\u00ecnh v\\u00f2ng cung d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u00ean b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t h\\u1ed3 r\\u1ed9ng 100 m, s\\u00e2u 1 m c\\u00f9ng nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1nh c\\u1ed5ng v\\u00f2m t\\u1ef1a m\\u1ed9t con t\\u00e0u kh\\u00f4ng gian. Khi c\\u1eeda t\\u00e0u m\\u1edf ra,\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/chu-de\\/sieu-mau-minh-tu-5787\\\" rel=\\\"dofollow\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_BoSuuTap-4591013&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-MinhTu&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">Minh T\\u00fa<\\/a>\\u00a0- v\\u00e0o vai sinh v\\u1eadt xinh \\u0111\\u1eb9p \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean - xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7m xuy\\u00ean th\\u1ea5u l\\u00e0m t\\u1eeb ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u t\\u00e1i ch\\u1ebf. Si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu ch\\u1ea1y nhanh l\\u00ean b\\u1eadc th\\u1ec1m, \\u0111\\u00f3n \\u00e1nh m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi. Sau c\\u00f4, t\\u1eebng nh\\u00f3m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu s\\u1ea3i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7m su\\u00f4ng \\u00f4m c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i, v\\u1eeba v\\u1eb7n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/chu-de\\/nha-thiet-ke-chung-thanh-phong-5201\\\" rel=\\\"dofollow\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_BoSuuTap-4591013&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-ChungThanhPhong&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">Chung Thanh Phong<\\/a> m\\u1ea5t ba th\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh 85 b\\u1ed9 trang ph\\u1ee5c cho show di\\u1ec5n. B\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chia th\\u00e0nh hai ph\\u1ea7n: thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng, phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n gi\\u1edbi h\\u1ea1n. N\\u1ebfu ph\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u, c\\u00e1c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu catwalk tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n nh\\u1ea1c s\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, \\u1edf ph\\u1ea7n hai, s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ecbch t\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ea9y l\\u00ean khi th\\u00e1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ed5 t\\u1eeb tr\\u00ean cao xu\\u1ed1ng. Show di\\u1ec5n g\\u00e2y \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u1edbi hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, n\\u1ec1n tr\\u1eddi chuy\\u1ec3n m\\u00e0u t\\u1eeb xanh sang h\\u1ed3ng. S\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n ng\\u1eadp n\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi\\u1ebfn hai ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tu\\u1ed9t gi\\u00e0y, nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c catwalk b\\u1eb1ng ch\\u00e2n tr\\u1ea7n, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c kh\\u00e1n gi\\u1ea3 v\\u1ed7 tay c\\u1ed5 v\\u0169.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/08\\/batch-0253FV5-foto-KIENGCAN-jp-9883-5477-1680935380.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=a5P2sxr0V7XXs-oncNzXcg\\\" alt=\\\"\\u0110\\u1ea7m metallic h\\u1edf l\\u01b0ng ph\\u1ed1i khuy\\u00ean v\\u00e0nh tai m\\u1ea1 kim lo\\u1ea1i. \\u1ea2nh: Ki\\u1ebfng C\\u1eadn Team\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110i theo h\\u01a1i h\\u01b0\\u1edbng Futuristic, b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng gam m\\u00e0u ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea1o \\u00e1nh kim xen k\\u1ebd tr\\u1eafng, \\u0111en v\\u00e0 xanh d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf khai th\\u00e1c tri\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u metallic, kim lo\\u1ea1i, l\\u01b0\\u1edbi, denim, da b\\u00f3ng. \\u00c1o v\\u00e1y ch\\u1ea7n b\\u00f4ng t\\u1eeb v\\u1ea3i thun \\u00e9p nh\\u0169, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p thun x\\u1ed1p 3D t\\u1ea1o hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng n\\u1ed5i. V\\u1edbi v\\u1ea3i d\\u00f9, trang ph\\u1ee5c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng gam m\\u00e0u \\u00e1nh b\\u1ea1c v\\u00e0 hologram, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean n\\u00e9t hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Phong c\\u00e1ch streetwear h\\u01a1i th\\u1edf Y2K g\\u00e2y b\\u00e3o tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi hai n\\u0103m qua \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng tri\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 trong b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp qua nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o denim k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p d\\u00e2y x\\u00edch, kim b\\u0103ng, t\\u1ea1o \\u00e2m h\\u01b0\\u1edfng punk, v\\u00e1y \\u00e1o h\\u00ecnh c\\u00e1nh b\\u01b0\\u1edbm. Chung Thanh Phong cho bi\\u1ebft anh mu\\u1ed1n tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi ph\\u00e2n kh\\u00fac gi\\u00e1 t\\u1ea7m trung, gi\\u00fap \\u0111\\u1ebfn g\\u1ea7n v\\u1edbi gen Z.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">B\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp c\\u00f2n mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7m su\\u00f4ng b\\u1eb1ng ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u kim lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1edbi hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng loang m\\u00e0u k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p kh\\u00f3a paracord, hay k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt in m\\u00e0u mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb cho metallic.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/08\\/batch-0260FV5-foto-KIENGCAN-jp-7527-6937-1680935381.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=XCtzMoxd0IR_HySmIzSIsQ\\\" alt=\\\"Trang ph\\u1ee5c denim h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng gen Z. \\u1ea2nh: Ki\\u1ebfng C\\u1eadn Team\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Corset - m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng phom d\\u00e1ng s\\u1edf tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a Chung Thanh Phong nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m qua - ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd theo phong c\\u00e1ch m\\u1edbi. Th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng cut-out, v\\u00e1y v\\u00e0 \\u00e1o corset tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1eafc n\\u00e9t, \\u0111\\u1ee9ng phom h\\u01a1n, t\\u00f4n c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eb7c. Draping v\\u00e0 x\\u1ebfp nh\\u00fan th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng ng\\u1eabu nhi\\u00ean tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf da b\\u00f3ng \\u0111em t\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1 v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ecb gi\\u00e1c. \\u0110\\u00ednh c\\u01b0\\u1eddm \\u1ed1ng, m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt kh\\u00f3, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a l\\u00ean c\\u00e1c b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7m d\\u00e1ng c\\u1ed9t, d\\u00e1ng su\\u00f4ng, mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng b\\u00f3ng m\\u01b0\\u1edbt. Tr\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng trang ph\\u1ee5c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00e1ng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, Chung Thanh Phong k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1eaft laser, t\\u1ea1o th\\u00e0nh nh\\u1eefng hoa v\\u0103n b\\u1eaft m\\u1eaft.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">M\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m\\u1edbi trong show di\\u1ec5n l\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y ph\\u1ea3i k\\u1ec3 t\\u1edbi ho\\u1ea1 ti\\u1ebft monogram \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Chung Thanh Phong x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u1ea7m d\\u00e1ng su\\u00f4ng, \\u00f4m c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1eeba ph\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 d\\u1ec5 m\\u1eb7c trong nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh. C\\u00e1c hoa v\\u0103n ch\\u1eef l\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean kh\\u00e9o l\\u00e9o t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng h\\u1ea1t c\\u01b0\\u1eddm, h\\u00f2a v\\u00e0o xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng chung c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e0ng m\\u1ed1t th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi v\\u00e0i n\\u0103m tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2023\\/04\\/08\\/batch-0117FV5-foto-KIENGCAN-jp-8711-4515-1680935381.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=EtBA1y8xGR8vbWA4Yh3Obg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00e2n kh\\u1ea5u v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng m\\u00e1i v\\u00f2m mang phong c\\u00e1ch t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai. \\u1ea2nh: Ki\\u1ebfng C\\u1eadn Team\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf n\\u1eafm b\\u1eaft xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng th\\u1eddi trang b\\u1ec1n v\\u1eefng, \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng tr\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7m l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n. Ch\\u00fang \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c s\\u1ee3i v\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ec9 th\\u1eeba x\\u00e9 nhuy\\u1ec5n, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p keo th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00e2n hu\\u1ef7. Trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o h\\u00ecnh b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u01b0\\u1edbm tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ean c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\"><em>CTPNo2<\\/em> c\\u00f2n cho th\\u1ea5y s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 khi \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 in 3D FDM, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean c\\u00e1c b\\u1ed9 khuy\\u00ean tai, \\u00e1o gi\\u00e1p. Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf cho bi\\u1ebft anh m\\u1ea5t 36 ti\\u1ebfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u1ea1n in 3D k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p m\\u1ea1 kim lo\\u1ea1i, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng th\\u1ecb gi\\u00e1c, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi gi\\u1eef \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ed9 nh\\u1eb9 cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m.<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:30:33\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:30:33\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:30:33\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(14, 'com_content.article.10', '', '2024-12-20 15:34:58', 642, 11659, 'fb2eb567cfd7921fe5915be190730e9999140c56', '{\"id\":10,\"asset_id\":127,\"title\":\"N\\u0103m d\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5n c\\u1ee7a show Fashion Voyage \\u1edf H\\u1ea1 Long\",\"alias\":\"nam-d-u-n-c-a-show-fashion-voyage-h-long\",\"introtext\":\"<p>V\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n th\\u1eddi trang v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u1edfng ngo\\u1ea1n du l\\u1ecbch, show t\\u1ed1i 18\\/5 thu h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi khi gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1eafc.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p><strong>\\u0110\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n th\\u1eddi trang<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tho\\u00e1t kh\\u1ecfi s\\u1ef1 g\\u00f2 b\\u00f3 tr\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng b\\u0103ng th\\u1eb3ng t\\u1eafp, \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan c\\u00f9ng 5 nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n khi \\u0111\\u01b0a b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp Cruise hay Resort 2020 \\u0111\\u1ebfn V\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long, l\\u00e0m n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\\"L\\u1ea1c gi\\u1eefa k\\u1ef3 quan\\\".\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fashion Voyage mong mu\\u1ed1n th\\u1ed5i l\\u00e0n gi\\u00f3 m\\u1edbi v\\u00e0o th\\u1eddi trang Vi\\u1ec7t, nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti\\u00ean phong c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e0ng m\\u1ed1t t\\u1eebng l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c: \\u0111\\u01b0a phong c\\u00e1ch c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh chu du kh\\u1eafp th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi. N\\u1ebfu Christian Dior \\u0111\\u00e1nh d\\u1ea5u l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u mang show Resort \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc Morocco xinh \\u0111\\u1eb9p th\\u00ec nh\\u00e0 m\\u1ed1t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc Ph\\u00e1p - Louis Vuitton - ra m\\u1eaft b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp Resort t\\u1ea1i New York (M\\u1ef9), hay Gucci tr\\u1edf v\\u1ec1 v\\u1edbi qu\\u00ea h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Italy... V\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\\"d\\u1ec7t m\\u1ed9ng vi\\u1ec5n du\\\" c\\u1ee7a \\u00eakip Fashion Voyage.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>S\\u00e0n runway th\\u00f4 m\\u1ed9c tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea3o \\\"Tr\\u00e1i tim\\\"<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fashion Voyage g\\u00e2y t\\u00f2 m\\u00f2 v\\u1edbi gi\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9 \\u0111i\\u1ec7u t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c show. B\\u00e3i B\\u00e0n Ch\\u00e2n (v\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long) mang v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p hoang s\\u01a1, th\\u01a1 m\\u1ed9ng. Nh\\u00ecn t\\u1eeb tr\\u00ean cao, h\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u00e1 c\\u00f3 h\\u00ecnh tr\\u00e1i tim.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1edbi mong mu\\u1ed1n l\\u00e0m n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh \\\"k\\u1ef3 quan trong l\\u00f2ng k\\u1ef3 quan\\\", ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf s\\u00e0n runway m\\u00f4 ph\\u1ecfng h\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea5u ch\\u00e2n in tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1t u\\u1ed1n l\\u01b0\\u1ee3n d\\u00e0i h\\u01a1n 100m. Nh\\u1eefng m\\u1ea3nh g\\u1ed7 th\\u00f4 m\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eafp x\\u1ebfp n\\u1eb1m trong kh\\u00f4ng gian giao thoa gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1t tr\\u1eafng, bi\\u1ec3n xanh, n\\u00fai non h\\u00f9ng v\\u0129.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/06\\/05\\/2-1559708100-8131-1559708313.png?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=fEBLrg-XSenvuSnSNhnt6A\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00e0n catwalk h\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0n ch\\u00e2n n\\u1ea5p m\\u00ecnh b\\u00ean h\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u00e1i Tim.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p nh\\u00e2n v\\u0103n<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Fashion Voyage m\\u00f9a hai nh\\u1eb1m truy\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3i th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p nh\\u00e2n v\\u0103n: b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 c\\u1ea3nh quan thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean. C\\u00e1c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu, nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi c\\u00f9ng d\\u1ecdn r\\u00e1c quanh \\u0111\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c, th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n \\u00fd th\\u1ee9c, tinh th\\u1ea7n tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m g\\u00ecn gi\\u1eef danh th\\u1eafng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan c\\u00f2n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u t\\u00e1i ch\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0 gi\\u1ea5y carton \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u1ef1ng b\\u1ed1i c\\u1ea3nh. Nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e2y x\\u01b0\\u01a1ng r\\u1ed3ng n\\u1edf hoa tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1t th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p lu\\u00f4n v\\u1eefng tin trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n kh\\u1eafc nghi\\u1ec7t, cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng v\\u1eabn th\\u0103ng hoa b\\u1edfi nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u \\u00fd ngh\\u0129a.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/06\\/05\\/4-1559708114-7058-1559708313.png?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=mIAR00LrNN_RxI0PDx2IvQ\\\" alt=\\\"X\\u01b0\\u01a1ng r\\u1ed3ng n\\u1edf hoa tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1t tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu catwalk.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M\\u1edf m\\u00e0n show th\\u1eddi trang, si\\u00eau m\\u1eabu Ho\\u00e0ng Th\\u00f9y xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n trong b\\u1ed9 v\\u00e1y tr\\u1eafng v\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ed1i xay gi\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng. Th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p v\\u1ec1 b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u00f4ng qua ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng v\\u00e0 khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c truy\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3i s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, ph\\u1ea7n tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n mapping hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng 3D tr\\u00ean v\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e1 t\\u00e1i hi\\u1ec7n huy\\u1ec1n tho\\u1ea1i H\\u1ea1 Long, di s\\u1ea3n thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean c\\u00f9ng t\\u00e0i nguy\\u00ean r\\u1eebng v\\u00e0ng, bi\\u1ec3n b\\u1ea1c. T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 kh\\u01a1i g\\u1ee3i t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau, ni\\u1ec1m t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o. \\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n 3D \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n gi\\u1eefa V\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long - n\\u01a1i Unesco c\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eadn l\\u00e0 Di s\\u1ea3n thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/06\\/05\\/5-1559708129-7935-1559708313.png?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=X44_c7sH1GYqo33dlj_T-Q\\\" alt=\\\"\\u00c1 h\\u1eadu Ho\\u00e0ng Th\\u00f9y l\\u00e0 g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t m\\u1edf m\\u00e0n c\\u1ee7a Fashion Voyage 2.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>\\u0110\\u1eb7c quy\\u1ec1n d\\u00e0nh cho kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ngo\\u00e0i theo d\\u00f5i c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a L\\u00e2m Gia Khang, H\\u00e0 Nh\\u1eadt Ti\\u1ebfn, Nguy\\u1ec5n Ti\\u1ebfn Truy\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 Younhee Park (H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c), Fashion Voyage mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t khi bi\\u1ebfn sundeck du thuy\\u1ec1n sang tr\\u1ecdng th\\u00e0nh s\\u00e0n catwalk di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng gi\\u1eefa V\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long. BST Aquafina x Ho\\u00e0ng Minh H\\u00e0 l\\u1ea5y c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u01b0\\u01a1i m\\u00e1t t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf g\\u1ee3i v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng, thanh l\\u1ecbch v\\u00e0 g\\u1ee3i c\\u1ea3m.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/06\\/05\\/ttttt-3221-1559708313.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=QcoTKGq_-WCV6nZu4EN2Og\\\" alt=\\\"BST Pure Aquafina x Ho\\u00e0ng Minh H\\u00e0 th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n tinh th\\u1ea7n t\\u1ef1 do, ph\\u00f3ng kho\\u00e1ng v\\u1edbi hai gam m\\u00e0u ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea1o tr\\u1eafng, xanh.\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>L\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean gi\\u1eefa v\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long, s\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec7n th\\u1eddi trang quy t\\u1ee5 4 chi\\u1ebfc du thuy\\u1ec1n sang tr\\u1ecdng President v\\u00e0 Paradise Cruise, \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u00f3n h\\u00e0ng tr\\u0103m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1eabu, hoa h\\u1eadu, kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sau chi\\u00eam ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng show th\\u1eddi trang, Paradise Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u01b0a kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi \\\"\\u0111\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ec7c\\\" \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, \\u00e2m nh\\u1ea1c v\\u00e0 \\u1ea9m th\\u1ef1c tr\\u00ean du thuy\\u1ec1n. Th\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u01a1n cho b\\u1eefa t\\u1ed1i do c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ebfp danh ti\\u1ebfng ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 John Burton Race - \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ebfp s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu nhi\\u1ec1u nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1eafn sao Michelin.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\\"sis_outstream__c\\\" data-set=\\\"dfp\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p>Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh thu h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u ngh\\u1ec7 s\\u0129 n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng nh\\u01b0: \\u0110\\u00e0m V\\u0129nh H\\u01b0ng, Minh H\\u1eb1ng, Hoa h\\u1eadu Thu\\u1ef3 Dung, \\u00c1 h\\u1eadu qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf Thu\\u00fd V\\u00e2n, ca s\\u0129 Tr\\u1ecdng Hi\\u1ebfu, ca s\\u0129 Orange... c\\u00f9ng lo\\u1ea1t fashionista Kh\\u00e1nh Linh the Face, stylist Kelbin Lei, Katleen Phan V\\u00f5...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 du l\\u1ecbch v\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n th\\u1eddi trang<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M\\u1ed1i duy\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a Paradise Vi\\u1ec7t Nam v\\u00e0 Fashion Voyage b\\u1eaft ngu\\u1ed3n t\\u1eeb s\\u1ee9 m\\u1ec7nh qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 du l\\u1ecbch v\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long. C\\u1ea3 hai \\u0111\\u1ec1u mong mu\\u1ed1n gi\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9 \\u0111i\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a di s\\u1ea3n thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi, \\u0111\\u01b0a H\\u1ea1 Long \\u0111\\u1ebfn g\\u1ea7n v\\u1edbi du kh\\u00e1ch.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sau Fashion Voyage s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean, c\\u1ea7u V\\u00e0ng B\\u00e0 N\\u00e0 Hills ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng h\\u00fat kh\\u00e1ch, do \\u0111\\u00f3 ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c k\\u1ef3 v\\u1ecdng b\\u00e3i B\\u00e0n Ch\\u00e2n - n\\u01a1i v\\u1ed1n v\\u1eafng v\\u1ebb - s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u00f3n nhi\\u1ec1u du kh\\u00e1ch trong v\\u00e0 ngo\\u00e0i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ebfn tham quan, th\\u01b0\\u1edfng ngo\\u1ea1n. Th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee7a show m\\u00f9a hai khi\\u1ebfn ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c c\\u00f3 th\\u00eam \\u0111\\u1ed9ng l\\u1ef1c l\\u00e0m ti\\u1ebfp c\\u00e1c m\\u00f9a ti\\u1ebfp theo.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:34:58\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:34:58\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:34:58\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link