(15, 'com_content.article.11', '', '2024-12-20 15:36:19', 642, 6961, '8a9e2adc778246aa8c4bf7d1ede74805cd6fabd8', '{\"id\":11,\"asset_id\":128,\"title\":\"Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c s\\u1ebd tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp \\u1edf H\\u1ea1 Long\",\"alias\":\"nha-thi-t-k-han-qu-c-s-trinh-di-n-b-suu-t-p-h-long\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Younhee Park gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp Xu\\u00e2n H\\u00e8 2019 trong show ngo\\u00e0i tr\\u1eddi c\\u1ee7a Long Kan.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan cho bi\\u1ebft Younhee Park tham gia show\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/giai-tri\\/thanh-hang-se-dien-thoi-trang-tren-dao-o-ha-long-3914616.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_LangMot-3924115&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-FashionVoyage&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">Fashion Voyage<\\/a>\\u00a0c\\u00f9ng b\\u1ed1n nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc: L\\u00e2m Gia Khang, H\\u00e0 Nh\\u1eadt Ti\\u1ebfn, Nguy\\u1ec5n Ti\\u1ebfn Truy\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 Ho\\u00e0ng Minh H\\u00e0.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Younhee Park t\\u1eebng tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n th\\u1eddi trang t\\u1ea1i H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i. Khi nghe Long Kan gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u1ec1\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/giai-tri\\/thanh-hang-se-dien-thoi-trang-tren-dao-o-ha-long-3914616.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-itm-source=\\\"#vn_source=Detail-GiaiTri_ThoiTrang_LangMot-3924115&amp;vn_campaign=Box-InternalLink&amp;vn_medium=Link-SanDien&amp;vn_term=Desktop&amp;vn_thumb=0\\\" data-itm-added=\\\"1\\\">s\\u00e0n di\\u1ec5n<\\/a>\\u00a0ngo\\u00e0i tr\\u1eddi t\\u1ea1i H\\u1ea1 Long, c\\u00f4 n\\u00f3i mu\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c\\u00a0gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp Xu\\u00e2n H\\u00e8 2019 \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2y.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u Greedilous do c\\u00f4 s\\u00e1ng l\\u1eadp v\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00e0nh \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c ng\\u00f4i sao h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u nh\\u01b0 Beyonce, Anne Hathaway, Paris Hilton \\u01b0a chu\\u1ed9ng... Th\\u1eddi gian g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e2y, Younhee Park th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u00ean truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00f4ng ch\\u00fang, gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb H\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 phong c\\u00e1ch thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf tr\\u1ebb trung, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/05\\/15\\/ntk-han-quoc-3068-1557914980.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=_5t0sZC5xh2NimR-ay5F-g\\\" alt=\\\"Nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Younhee Park\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">Younhee Park\\u00a0c\\u00f3 g\\u00f3c nh\\u00ecn th\\u1eddi trang \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng.\\u00a0Nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 c\\u00e1nh c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4 \\u0111i t\\u1eeb phong c\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng, n\\u1eef t\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ebfn ph\\u00e1 c\\u00e1ch v\\u00e0 t\\u00e1o b\\u1ea1o, c\\u00f9ng slogan th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n tinh th\\u1ea7n quy\\u1ebft li\\u1ec7t, t\\u1ef1 tin c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u1ebb. Younhee Park c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 nh\\u00e0 m\\u1ed1t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xuy\\u00ean g\\u00f3p m\\u1eb7t t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c Tu\\u1ea7n l\\u1ec5 th\\u1eddi trang danh gi\\u00e1 nh\\u01b0 Paris, New York, Seoul... C\\u00f4 c\\u0169ng nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ea7n \\\"b\\u1eaft tay\\\" v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u nh\\u01b0 Prada, MiuMiu, Givenchy... \\u0111\\u1ec3 cho ra b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp chung.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan chia s\\u1ebb: \\\"T\\u1eeb khi kh\\u1edfi x\\u01b0\\u1edbng Fashion Voyage, t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh h\\u01b0\\u1edbng m\\u1ed7i h\\u00e0nh tr\\u00ecnh s\\u1ebd m\\u1eddi \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ec3 qu\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1 du l\\u1ecbch Vi\\u1ec7t. \\u1ede s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean, t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u00e3 m\\u1eddi A Sai Ta \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb London. H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 kinh \\u0111\\u00f4 th\\u1eddi trang ch\\u00e2u \\u00c1, v\\u00ec v\\u1eady t\\u00f4i tin b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp c\\u1ee7a Younhee Park s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u00f3n nh\\u1eadn\\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net\\/2019\\/05\\/16\\/beyonce15-8442-1558007067.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=dwX66i89zBTxemetyHD7pQ\\\" alt=\\\"Beyonce di\\u1ec7n v\\u00e1y c\\u1ee7a Younhee Park.\\u00a0\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"Normal\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">Fashion Voyage m\\u00f9a hai s\\u1ebd di\\u1ec5n ra v\\u00e0o chi\\u1ec1u 18\\/5 t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea3o B\\u00e0n Ch\\u00e2n, v\\u1ecbnh H\\u1ea1 Long v\\u1edbi 100 kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1eddi. Chu\\u1ed7i ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh b\\u1eaft ngu\\u1ed3n t\\u1eeb \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p th\\u1eddi trang v\\u00e0 th\\u1ef1c c\\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea1o di\\u1ec5n Long Kan, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u1edf Vi\\u1ec7t Nam. Phong c\\u00e1ch n\\u00e0y \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Dior, Louis Vuitton... y\\u00eau th\\u00edch. S\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean di\\u1ec5n ra tr\\u00ean c\\u1ea7u V\\u00e0ng, B\\u00e0 N\\u00e0 m\\u00f9a h\\u00e8 n\\u0103m ngo\\u00e1i.<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2024-12-20 15:36:19\",\"created_by\":642,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-12-20 15:36:19\",\"modified_by\":642,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-12-20 15:36:19\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\